cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with depth estimation from a single image using convolutional neural networks. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes an end-to-end trainable network for depth estimation. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses attention mechanism to fuse multi-scale features produced in DFE. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as depth estimation is an important task in robotics for navigation and obstacle avoidance. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as depth estimation is an important task in multimedia applications such as virtual reality and augmented reality.
